# 🛍️ Customer Segmentation using K-Means Clustering

## 📌 SkillCraft Technology – Machine Learning Internship

### Task 02

This project was completed as part of the **SkillCraft Technology Machine Learning Internship**.

The objective of this project is to segment customers of a retail store using the **K-Means Clustering** algorithm based on their purchasing behavior.

---

## 📊 Dataset

**Mall Customer Segmentation Dataset**

Features Used:

- Annual Income (k$)
- Spending Score (1–100)

Dataset:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/vjchoudhary7/customer-segmentation-tutorial-in-python

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- Python
- Google Colab
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Scikit-learn
- Pickle

---

## 📈 Workflow

- Imported required libraries
- Loaded the dataset
- Explored and visualized the data
- Encoded categorical values
- Applied the Elbow Method
- Built the K-Means Clustering model
- Visualized customer clusters
- Saved the trained model
- Predicted customer clusters

